[{"title":"建立新的 hexo blog 並從現有的部落格複製","url":"/2020/12/16/202012/20201216-CreateNewHexoBlog/","content":"<div class=\"note default\">\n            <p>建立新的 hexo blog 並從現有的部落格複製</p>\n          </div>\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"安裝-Hexo\"><a href=\"#安裝-Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝 Hexo\"></a>安裝 Hexo</h2><p>使用指令安裝 Hexo，開啟終端機 (cmd)輸入以下指令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"架設-hexo\"><a href=\"#架設-hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"架設 hexo\"></a>架設 hexo</h2><ol>\n<li>打開 cmd 執行以下指令<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> D:\\Blog</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init HankMemoCopy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>刪掉 D:\\Blog\\HankMemoCopy\\ 裡面的所有資料夾及檔案 並從現有的 GSSWorkLog 複製 ( 但不包含 [public] 資料夾與 db.json )</li>\n<li>刪掉備份用的資料夾與檔案 [_bak] 資料夾、ZIP_node_modules.zip.txt、ZIP_themes.zip.txt</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"連動git\"><a href=\"#連動git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"連動git\"></a>連動git</h2><ol>\n<li>登入bitbucket</li>\n<li>右上角按鈕 Create repository <ul>\n<li>Untitled project</li>\n<li>Include .gitignore? = Yes</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>git clone<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/hccga7/hankmemocopy/src/master/\">https://bitbucket.org/hccga7/hankmemocopy/src/master/</a></li>\n<li>D:\\Blog\\HankMemoCopy\\</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>解壓縮複製回 D:\\Blog\\HankMemoCopy\\ ( 取代 .gitignore )</li>\n<li>git add commit</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>上述步驟預設不含 db.json 及 node_modules 整個資料夾<br>為求能不同電腦同步，此處將 node_modules 整個資料夾加入<br>即 .gitignore 這個檔案拿掉 node_modules/ 這一行<br>然後將 node_modules 整個資料夾 git add commit</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"開始使用\"><a href=\"#開始使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"開始使用\"></a>開始使用</h2><ul>\n<li><p>登入其他電腦，試用 bitbucket<br>啟動網頁後出現 Cannot GET / 的問題<br>整包壓縮備份 整個資料夾備份蓋過新電腦中的同一個資料夾，之後就正常了</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>參考文章<br><a href=\"https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/questions/10189105\">node Cannot GET /</a><br><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/9627441/cannot-get-with-connect-on-node-js\">“Cannot GET /” with Connect on Node.js</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在surface電腦上<br>調整ShellIconOverLay (無效)<br>改搬至本機硬碟(不要用SD卡)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"指定-hexo-port\"><a href=\"#指定-hexo-port\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"指定 hexo port\"></a>指定 hexo port</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s -p 9000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://programmer.ink/think/from-build-to-deploy-build-a-private-blog-quickly.html\">From build to deploy, build a private blog quickly</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"參考文章\"><a href=\"#參考文章\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"參考文章\"></a>參考文章</h2><p><a href=\"https://hsiangfeng.github.io/hexo/20190411/932826160/\">架設 Hexo+GitHub</a><br><a href=\"https://hsuchihting.github.io/hexo/20191217/1291925723/\">第一次建立 Hexo 與推上 GitHub</a></p>\n","categories":["技術","hexo"],"tags":["hexo"]},{"title":"使用 GoogleVisionApi 相關的 Auth 及備忘事項","url":"/2020/12/16/202012/20201216-GoogleVisionApi_Auth/","content":"<div class=\"note default\">\n            <p>GoogleVisionApi 的使用與環境變數</p>\n          </div>\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"重要步驟\"><a href=\"#重要步驟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重要步驟\"></a>重要步驟</h2><ol>\n<li>用 cmd 建立 .net core 專案</li>\n<li>相依性引入 Google.Cloud.Vision.V1</li>\n<li>從 google console 匯出 my-key.json</li>\n<li>設定環境變數<ul>\n<li>檔案總管</li>\n<li>本機 - 右鍵 - 內容 - (最右邊)進階系統設定 - (方框)環境變數<br><img src=\"/2020/12/16/202012/20201216-GoogleVisionApi_Auth/explorer1.png\" alt=\"explorer1\"></li>\n<li>自行新增/編輯一個 GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS 變數<br><img src=\"/2020/12/16/202012/20201216-GoogleVisionApi_Auth/explorer2.png\" alt=\"explorer2\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"程式範例\"><a href=\"#程式範例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"程式範例\"></a>程式範例</h2><p><a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/hccga7/hccga7/src/master/side_proj/2020/VisionApiDemo/\">VisionApiDemo</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"使用-powershell-檢視所有環境變數\"><a href=\"#使用-powershell-檢視所有環境變數\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用 powershell 檢視所有環境變數\"></a>使用 powershell 檢視所有環境變數</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gci env:* | sort-object name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["技術","google"],"tags":["google","api"]},{"title":"使用自行包裝的 AzureCognitiveServicesTTS 以及 Task 初探","url":"/2020/12/16/202012/20201216-AzureCognitiveServicesTTSAndTask/","content":"<div class=\"note default\">\n            <p>Azure CognitiveServices 文字朗讀功能 且有部份與 Task 相關</p>\n          </div>\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"SynthesisToSpeakerAsyncWrap-程式\"><a href=\"#SynthesisToSpeakerAsyncWrap-程式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SynthesisToSpeakerAsyncWrap 程式\"></a>SynthesisToSpeakerAsyncWrap 程式</h2><figure class=\"highlight cs\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">async</span> Task <span class=\"title\">SynthesisToSpeakerAsyncWrap</span>(<span class=\"params\"><span class=\"keyword\">string</span> text, <span class=\"keyword\">string</span> tts_path</span>)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">string</span> apiKey = <span class=\"string\">&quot;7340d2aa57254ee994003fb7ad262557&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">string</span> apiRegion = <span class=\"string\">&quot;southeastasia&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">string</span> voiceName = <span class=\"string\">&quot;zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">await</span> HankTool2020.Azure.CognitiveServicesTTS.SynthesisToSpeakerAsync(apiKey, apiRegion, voiceName, text, tts_path);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            Console.WriteLine(text);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 以下是主程式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            sArr = <span class=\"string\">@&quot;C:\\TestArea\\G0380001_TestLoop\\&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">string</span> saveWavPath = <span class=\"string\">@&quot;C:\\TestArea\\G0380001_wav\\&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">string</span>[] textLawArray = Directory.GetFiles(sArr);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">foreach</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">string</span> s <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> textLawArray)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">string</span> path = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> FileInfo(s).Name;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                path = saveWavPath + path + <span class=\"string\">&quot;.wav&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                path = path.Replace(<span class=\"string\">&quot;.txt&quot;</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">string</span>.Empty);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">string</span> text = File.ReadAllText(s, Encoding.UTF8);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                SynthesisToSpeakerAsyncWrap(text, path).Wait();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"問題說明\"><a href=\"#問題說明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"問題說明\"></a>問題說明</h2><ul>\n<li>原本沒找到 .Wait(); 之前，程式執行時是非同步的，可能是一次執行多個，在使用 api 時會出現錯誤，也無法正常轉檔/儲存檔案</li>\n<li>後來找到以下參考文章，就可以讓每次迴圈中的 Task 跑完再到下個迴圈<br><a href=\"https://csharpkh.blogspot.com/2019/09/CSharp-Task-Run-StartNew-Thread-Wait-Cancellation-CancellationToken-Exception.html\">當使用工作執行個體，如何等待該執行完成</a></li>\n<li>自製的元件<br><a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/hccga7/hccga7/src/master/HankTool2020/Azure/\">HankTool2020.Azure.CognitiveServicesTTS</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"官方網頁語音清單\"><a href=\"#官方網頁語音清單\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"官方網頁語音清單\"></a>官方網頁語音清單</h2><p><a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/zh-tw/services/cognitive-services/text-to-speech/#features\">文字轉換語音</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"建議採用之語音\"><a href=\"#建議採用之語音\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建議採用之語音\"></a>建議採用之語音</h3><p>繁中: zh-TW-HsiaoChenNeural<br>英文: en-US-JennyNeural</p>\n<h2 id=\"延伸學習-欲購清單\"><a href=\"#延伸學習-欲購清單\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"延伸學習 (欲購清單)\"></a>延伸學習 (欲購清單)</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/course/introduction-to-concurrency-in-c-async-and-paralellism/\">Introduction to Concurrency in C# - Async and Paralellism</a></p>\n","categories":["技術","azure"],"tags":["api","azure"]},{"title":"VMWare 安裝 Linux 之記錄及備忘事項 ( 主要是 openSUSE )","url":"/2020/12/16/202012/20201216-LinuxOpenSuse/","content":"<div class=\"note default\">\n            <p>VMWare 安裝 Linux 之記錄及備忘事項 (含嘸蝦米輸入法)</p>\n          </div>\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<h2 id=\"VMwareTools-更新-安裝過程全用預設值\"><a href=\"#VMwareTools-更新-安裝過程全用預設值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"VMwareTools 更新 (安裝過程全用預設值)\"></a>VMwareTools 更新 (安裝過程全用預設值)</h2><h3 id=\"步驟一\"><a href=\"#步驟一\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"步驟一\"></a>步驟一</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">tar -zxvf VMwareTools-10.3.21-14772444.tar.gz -C /tmp</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> /tmp/vmware-tools-distrib</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo ./vmware-install.pl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.itread01.com/p/1377180.html\">VMWare Tools 和 Shared folder（共享資料夾）</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"步驟二-無報錯即表示成功，檔案總管需重開\"><a href=\"#步驟二-無報錯即表示成功，檔案總管需重開\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"步驟二 (無報錯即表示成功，檔案總管需重開)\"></a>步驟二 (無報錯即表示成功，檔案總管需重開)</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo vmhgfs-fuse .host:/ /mnt/hgfs -o subtype=vmhgfs-fuse,allow_other</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ls /mnt/hgfs</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/hcu5555/article/details/107182222\">kali2020挂载共享文件夹（挂载hgfs共享文件）</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"步驟三-編輯-fstab-檔案\"><a href=\"#步驟三-編輯-fstab-檔案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"步驟三 編輯 fstab 檔案\"></a>步驟三 編輯 fstab 檔案</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo nano /etc/fstab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>結果參考如下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight txt\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /                       btrfs  defaults                      0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /var                    btrfs  subvol=/@/var                 0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /usr/local              btrfs  subvol=/@/usr/local           0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /srv                    btrfs  subvol=/@/srv                 0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /root                   btrfs  subvol=/@/root                0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /opt                    btrfs  subvol=/@/opt                 0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /home                   btrfs  subvol=/@/home                0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /boot/grub2/x86_64-efi  btrfs  subvol=/@/boot/grub2/x86_64-efi  0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /boot/grub2/i386-pc     btrfs  subvol=/@/boot/grub2/i386-pc  0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=0f4ae7dd-1572-49c8-8849-dde58db9b6a7  /.snapshots             btrfs  subvol=/@/.snapshots          0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\">UUID=7c1839cf-5194-4a36-9470-2b7c2c4ff2f9  swap                    swap   defaults                      0  0</span><br><span class=\"line\"># mount hgfs</span><br><span class=\"line\">.host:/       /mnt/hgfs        fuse.vmhgfs-fuse       allow_other     0       0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"調整開機時倒數等待之預設時間\"><a href=\"#調整開機時倒數等待之預設時間\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"調整開機時倒數等待之預設時間\"></a>調整開機時倒數等待之預設時間</h2><p>1.導​​航到Yast-&gt;系統-&gt; Bootloader<br>2.單擊Bootloader安裝選項卡，然後單擊Boot Loader選項按鈕<br>3.在“秒數超時”字段下，更改從8秒到2秒之間的數字<br>4.單擊OK（確定）按鈕應用更改<br><a href=\"https://forums.opensuse.org/showthread.php/412324-How-to-make-GRUB-countdown-shorter\">How to make GRUB countdown shorter?</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"安裝無蝦米-嘸蝦米\"><a href=\"#安裝無蝦米-嘸蝦米\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安裝無蝦米 (嘸蝦米)\"></a>安裝無蝦米 (嘸蝦米)</h2><h3 id=\"重要步驟\"><a href=\"#重要步驟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重要步驟\"></a>重要步驟</h3><p>1.解壓縮得出 noseeing.gtab<br>2.安裝gcin (yast)<br>3.開啟Kansole sudo cp noseeing.gtab /usr/share/gcin/table (無法直接用檔案總管複製)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">zypper install gcc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"字典檔備份\"><a href=\"#字典檔備份\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字典檔備份\"></a>字典檔備份</h3><p>/2020/12/16/202012/20201216-LinuxOpenSuse/noseeing.gtab</p>\n<h3 id=\"參考文章複製\"><a href=\"#參考文章複製\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"參考文章複製\"></a>參考文章複製</h3><p>無蝦米安裝程序：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>於/etc/apt/sources.lst 加入這行<br>deb <a href=\"http://www.calno.com/\">http://www.calno.com</a> unstable main</li>\n<li>sudo apt-get update;sudo apt-get install gcin (安裝gcin)</li>\n<li>sudo im-switch -s gcin (下次登入即可使用gcin)</li>\n<li>wget <a href=\"http://edt1023.sayya.org/misc/noseeing-6.tar.gz\">http://edt1023.sayya.org/misc/noseeing-6.tar.gz</a> (下載無蝦米表格檔)</li>\n<li>tar zxvf noseeing-6.tar.gz</li>\n<li>sudo cp noseeing.gtab /usr/share/gcin/table/</li>\n<li>(system restart)<br><a href=\"https://blog.xuite.net/jiazhe/running/14152737\">Ubuntu gcin使用無蝦米輸入法</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"其他參考文章\"><a href=\"#其他參考文章\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"其他參考文章\"></a>其他參考文章</h3><p><a href=\"https://neroli.pixnet.net/blog/post/30476744\">電腦文 OpenSuse Server上安裝gcin中文輸入法</a><br><a href=\"https://www.ubuntu-tw.org/modules/newbb/viewtopic.php?post_id=360134\">請問在英文語系的ubuntu，無法輸入中文    論壇 - Ubuntu基本設定</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"PyCharm-Python-Debugger-Extension-未整理筆記\"><a href=\"#PyCharm-Python-Debugger-Extension-未整理筆記\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"PyCharm Python Debugger Extension 未整理筆記\"></a>PyCharm Python Debugger Extension 未整理筆記</h2><ul>\n<li>未安裝前，執行偵錯時會跳出提示，建議使用者安裝 Python Debugger Extension</li>\n<li>安裝的過程有些許繁瑣<br>2020-11-18<br>11:17    Python Debugger Extension Available<pre><code>      Cython extension speeds up Python debugging\n      Install   How does it work</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>install ok</p>\n<h2 id=\"Software-Updates-更新指令\"><a href=\"#Software-Updates-更新指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Software Updates 更新指令\"></a>Software Updates 更新指令</h2><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo zypper dup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["技術","linux"],"tags":["vmware","linux","opensuse","嘸蝦米","pycharm"]}]